OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny overnight fog and low cloud
OL,6,Fdispersing this morning. Otherwise it
OL,7,Fwill be dry with plenty of sunshine.
OL,8,FWarm, but cooler along the east coast.
OL,9,
OL,10,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry with
OL,11,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,12,Fthe night will be dry and clear with
OL,13,Fsome patchy fog and low cloud. Patchy
OL,14,Ffrost.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FDry with some sunshine in the
OL,17,Fmorning. Clouding over from the
OL,18,Fsouthwest in the afternoon with some
OL,19,Fshowery rain extending northeast
OL,20,Flater. Warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
